C $BCE1,2 Is the supertile index < 139?
C $BCE3,2 Jump if so
C $BCE5,2 Is the supertile index >= 204?
C $BCE7,2 Jump if so
C $BCE9,3 Point #REGbc at exterior_tiles[145 + 220]
@ $BCEC label=sts_exit
