C $CCF1,2 Jump to next iteration if so
C $CCF3,2 Is it item_FOOD?
C $CCF5,2 Jump to next iteration if so
C $CCF7,3 Otherwise, hostiles pursue prisoners
C $CCFA,1 Return
;
c $CCFB Is item discoverable (interior)
