C $DC8E,3 Fetch an address
C $DC91,1 Write a new opcode
C $DC92,1 Advance
C $DC93,3 Fetch an address
C $DC96,1 Advance
C $DC97,1 Write a new opcode
C $DC98,1 Count down the counter
